OL,3,CPolice officers who pepper-sprayed and
OL,4,Ctasered amputee found not guilty
OL,6,FAfter the verdict, Mavi Salvatori, a
OL,7,Frepresentative of Bhatt Murphy
OL,8,FSolicitors, read a statement on behalf
OL,9,Fof Donald Burgess' family.
OL,11,FTwo police officers who used a Taser
OL,12,Fand synthetic pepper spray on a one-
OL,13,Flegged 92-year-old man have been
OL,14,Fcleared of assault.
OL,16,FPc Stephen Smith, 51, and Pc Rachel
OL,17,FComotto, 36, were accused of using
OL,18,Fexcessive force on Donald Burgess
OL,19,Fduring a confrontation at Park Beck
OL,20,Fcare home in St Leonards-on-Sea, East
OL,21,FSussex, in June 2022.
