OL,3,CPolice officers who pepper-sprayed and
OL,4,Ctasered amputee found not guilty
OL,6,FJurors returned their unanimous
OL,7,Fverdicts on both Sussex Police
OL,8,Fofficers at Southwark Crown Court
OL,9,Fafter around two hours of
OL,10,Fdeliberations on Wednesday.
OL,12,FThey found Smith not guilty of two
OL,13,Fcounts of assault occasioning actual
OL,14,Fbodily harm for his use of Pava spray
OL,15,Fand for using a baton, whilst Comotto
OL,16,Fwas found not guilty of one count for
OL,17,Fdeploying her Taser.
OL,19,FSussex Police, Assistant Chief
OL,20,FConstable Paul Court spoke outside the
OL,21,Fcourt after the verdict.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/16
