OL,3,CPolice officers who pepper-sprayed and
OL,4,Ctasered amputee found not guilty
OL,6,FBoth officers will however face
OL,7,Fproceedings for gross misconduct,
OL,8,FAssistant Chief Constable Paul Court,
OL,9,Ffrom Sussex Police, said in a
OL,10,Fstatement he delivered outside court.
OL,12,FHe said: "I would like to acknowledge
OL,13,Fhow incredibly difficult this period
OL,14,Fmust have been for Mr Burgess's family
OL,15,Fand I offer them my sincere
OL,16,Fcondolences.
OL,18,F"I recognise and understand the impact
OL,19,Fthat this case has had on public
OL,20,Fconfidence.
OL,26,@tD@JOUzD@AOU
