OL,3,CPolice officers who pepper-sprayed and
OL,4,Ctasered amputee found not guilty
OL,6,F"It is with profound regret this
OL,7,Fhappened.
OL,9,F"Police officers can find themselves
OL,10,Fin challenging and unpredictable
OL,11,Fsituations where they must make split-
OL,12,Fsecond decisions to keep the public
OL,13,Fsafe, and to do so with measure,
OL,14,Fcompassion and skill.
OL,16,F"We support them to do this and this
OL,17,Fis what our communities expect.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUxD@AOU
