OL,6,FIOPC director Emily Barry said: "Our
OL,7,Fthoughts and sympathies remain with
OL,8,Fthe family of Donald Burgess.
OL,10,F"We know this case ` including the
OL,11,Fpolice body-worn footage that was
OL,12,Freleased during the trial ` has caused
OL,13,Funderstandable concern in the
OL,14,Fcommunity.
OL,16,F"It was right that the evidence was
OL,17,Fput before a jury so the officers
OL,18,Fcould be held accountable and we
OL,19,Frespect the jury's decision."
OL,26,@nD@aOUrD@AOUxD@AOU{D@]O]
