OL,6,FThe care home had called 999 after Mr
OL,7,FBurgess, a single-leg amputee and
OL,8,Fwheelchair user, reportedly grabbed a
OL,9,Fknife he was given to cut his food and
OL,10,Fthreatened to stab staff.
OL,12,FThe court previously heard this was
OL,13,F"out of character" for Mr Burgess,
OL,14,Fwhose movements with the knife were
OL,15,Fdescribed by deputy care home manager
OL,16,FDonna Gardner as "extremely quick".
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@RO]xD@ROUxD@bO]
