OL,4,Ctasered amputee found not guilty
OL,6,F"The reason for his behaviour that
OL,7,Fday, we now know, is that he was
OL,8,Fdelirious as a result of a urinary
OL,9,Ftract infection," judge Christopher
OL,10,FHehir told jurors.
OL,12,FSmith sprayed synthetic Pava pepper
OL,13,Fspray into Mr Burgess's face and used
OL,14,Fhis baton to try and knock the knife
OL,15,Fout of Mr Burgess's hand, with Comotto
OL,16,Fdeploying her Taser, all within a
OL,17,Fminute and 23 seconds of entering the
OL,18,Fwheelchair-bound pensioner's room.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@QO]
