OL,6,FMr Burgess was taken to hospital after
OL,7,Fthe incident and later contracted
OL,8,FCovid.
OL,10,FHe died 22 days later aged 93.
OL,12,FCare home manager Steve Cooper
OL,13,Fpreviously told jurors Burgess had
OL,14,Fbeen threatening staff for more than
OL,15,F30 minutes with a serrated knife
OL,16,Fbefore they decided to call 999.
OL,18,F"He was very aggressive and
OL,19,Fthreatening to hurt my members of
OL,20,Fstaff," he told the court.
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@GO]
