OL,6,F"We tried to use different de-
OL,7,Fescalation techniques. He wasn't
OL,8,Fresponding to anything we said.
OL,10,F"He had a look in his eyes I've never
OL,11,Fseen before ` he wasn't the Donald I
OL,12,Fknew."
OL,14,FHe said Mr Burgess jabbed the knife
OL,15,Ftowards him and told him: "I'm going
OL,16,Fto murder you, and I'll enjoy it."
