OL,6,FThe court heard both Smith and Comotto
OL,7,Frepeatedly asked Mr Burgess to drop
OL,8,Fthe knife, with Smith warning him:
OL,9,F"Put the knife down mate, or you will
OL,10,Fbe sprayed or tasered. That's up to
OL,11,Fyou."
OL,13,FFootage from body-worn cameras played
OL,14,Fto the jury during the trial showed
OL,15,FSmith then discharging the spray
OL,16,Fdirectly into Mr Burgess's face.
OL,18,FMr Burgess then raised the knife a
OL,19,Fcouple of times as Smith uses his
OL,20,Fbaton to try and get the knife out of
OL,21,Fhis hand.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@EO]
