OL,6,FWhen this failed, Comotto deployed her
OL,7,FTaser.
OL,9,FPc Smith previously told jurors he did
OL,10,Fnot see that Mr Burgess was disabled
OL,11,Fand using a wheelchair until after the
OL,12,Fincident as he was focused on the
OL,13,Fknife the pensioner was holding in his
OL,14,Fhand.
OL,16,FHe added he believed Mr Burgess "could
OL,17,Fclearly understand what we were saying
OL,18,Fto him" as Mr Burgess reportedly asked
OL,19,F"Are there many more of them coming?"
OL,20,F` suggesting he was aware Smith and
OL,21,FComotto were police officers.
