OL,6,FDuring his evidence, Pc Smith also
OL,7,Fdenied hitting Mr Burgess with a
OL,8,Fbaton, claiming he instead flicked the
OL,9,Fbaton towards the pensioner's wrist to
OL,10,F"knock the knife out" of his hand.
OL,12,FSmith said: "The way he had been
OL,13,Fthreatening staff members ` the threat
OL,14,Fwas the knife, to the staff there and
OL,15,Falso to himself.
OL,17,F"I just wanted the knife out of the
OL,18,Fgent's hand."
